    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName key="#Priests"><name>Atrifusu</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs> filio <persName>bone memorie
                                <name>Pascali</name></persName> riceve da <persName
                            ref="#people/214" key="#Bishops">Gherardus</persName>, gratia Dei huius
                        sancte Lucane ecclesie umilis <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>, per cartula
                        livellario nomine (…), usque in viginti et nove annos ecc. (…) una casa cum
                        fundamento et curte totum insimul foras muros istius civitatis, pertenentes
                        ecclesie <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/272" key="#Churches">Sancte
                            Marie</orgName>, prope <placeName ref="#places/4" key="#Clusae/gates"
                                ><rs key="#Clusae/gates">porta</rs> que dicitur Cervasi</placeName>,
                        que est de suppotestate ipsius epis(copatus) vestro; et ipsa casa cum
                        fundamento e (sic) curte tenentes uno capo cum uno lato in ter[ra …]
                        suprascripte eccl(esie) Sancti Cervasi, alio capo tenet in terra et
                        fundamento de casa […, et alio] lato tenet in via publica; suprascripta casa
                        cum fundamento et curte (…). La concessione a 29 anni è per Atrifuso pbr et
                        Flaiperto f. qd. Lopi, uno dei quali dovrà abitarvi (…). Censo: per
                        sing(ulos) annos in mense augusto a parte suprascripte eccl(esie) Sancte
                        Marie a custodem et rectorem eius (…) argen(tum) den(arios) quatuor boni
                        expend(ibiles) tentum; et a mandato vestro, vel de ipso custode et rectore
                        suprascripte eccl(esie) Sancte Marie venire ecc. hic Luca legem ecc. (…).
                        Pena: argen(tum) solid(os) viginti et omnes movilias nostras, que in
                        edeficio case sunt, in nostra vel de illo homines cui nos eas dederimus,
                        dedisti potestatem exinde tollendum et faciendum exinde quot volueriumus
                        (…). <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Petrus"
                            >Petrus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive due <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">cartulas</rs>. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4" key="#Cities #Churches #Mother_churches #Bishops"
                            >Luca</placeName>. </ab>
                    <ab>Sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>: <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name>Suntripaldo</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Ghisulfus">Ghisolfo</name> de <placeName
                                ref="#places/3112">vico Pelago</placeName></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Ghisulfus">Ghisolfo</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Teudaldus">Teudaldus</name></persName>.</ab>
                </div>
